document.full_text: video from the french ministry of defense shows the rescue of a japanese diplomat whose compound in ivory coast was raided by members of a militia loyal to the self-appointed president, laurent gbagbo.
document.title: the lede: french strike gbagbo defenders during rescue of japanese diplomat in ivory coast
